Package: structured
Title: A Tool To Create Structured R Projects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Giuseppe",
           family = "Tomio",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "g.tinti.tomio@gmail.com")
Description: A tool to create structured R projects. The projects can be
    created either interactively using the RStudio Project Templates
    feature, or programmatically using the structure_project function
    exported by this package.
